</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E97036DD3F19FF8EFF26FF3DFB3EFEFC" blockId="44.[151,1437,151,393]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
Habitat. Circalittoral, on 
<taxonomicName id="2ECF4D5E3F19FF8EFE3EFF3DFD93FF34" authorityName="Decaisne" authorityYear="1841" box="[479,627,187,213]" family="Peyssonneliaceae" genus="Peyssonnelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Cryptonemiales" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" phylum="Rhodophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="DBBBEACF3F19FF8EFE3EFF3DFD93FF34" box="[479,627,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Peyssonnelia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and maerl red algae beds, coarse sand and deep-sea oyster shell remains bottoms from around 
<quantity id="2E379B383F19FF8EFE6AFF58FE24FF18" box="[395,452,222,249]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" unit="m" value="50.0">50 m</quantity>
to 
<quantity id="2E379B383F19FF8EFE06FF59FDCDFF18" box="[487,557,223,249]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.16" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" unit="m" value="116.0">116 m</quantity>
depth (
<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F19FF8EFD60FF59FC8EFF18" author="Kovacic, M. &amp; Ordines, F. &amp; Schliewen, U." box="[641,878,223,249]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="447 - 460" refId="ref59146" refString="Kovacic, M., Ordines, F. &amp; Schliewen, U. (2017 a) A new species of Buenia (Teleostei: Gobiidae) from the western Mediterranean Sea, with the description of this genus. Zootaxa, 4050 (5), 447 - 460. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4250.5.3" type="journal article" year="2017">
Kovačić 
<emphasis id="DBBBEACF3F19FF8EFD06FF59FCF8FF18" box="[743,792,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">et al</emphasis>
. 2017a
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F19FF8EFC98FF59FBBFFF18" author="Ordines, F. &amp; Kovacic, M. &amp; Vivas, M. &amp; Garcia-Ruiz, C. &amp; Guijarro, B." box="[889,1119,223,249]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="275 - 282" refId="ref62095" refString="Ordines, F., Kovacic, M., Vivas, M., Garcia-Ruiz, C. &amp; Guijarro, B. (2019 a) Westernmost Mediterranean records of three gobiid species (Actinopterygii: Perciformes: Gobiidae). Acta Ichthyologica et Piscatoria, 49, 275 - 282. https: // doi. org / 10.3750 / AIEP / 02604" type="journal article" year="2019">
Ordines 
<emphasis id="DBBBEACF3F19FF8EFC38FF59FBEAFF18" box="[985,1034,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">et al</emphasis>
. 2019a
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F19FF8EFB8BFF59FB56FF1B" author="Ordines, F. &amp; Ramirez-Amaro, S. &amp; Burgos C. &amp; Baro, J. &amp; Kovacic, M. &amp; Sobrino, I." box="[1130,1206,223,250]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" pagination="85 - 89" refId="ref62161" refString="Ordines, F., Ramirez-Amaro, S. Burgos C., Baro, J., Kovacic, M. &amp; Sobrino, I. (2019 b) First record of Buenia massutii Kovacic, Ordines, &amp; Schliewen, 2017 in the Atlantic Ocean based on molecular and morphological evidences. Journal of Applied Ichthyology, 36, 85 - 89. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / jai. 13985" type="journal article" year="2019">2019b</bibRefCitation>
). A small individual photographed at 
<quantity id="2E379B383F19FF8EFEB2FE85FE6CFEFC" box="[339,396,259,285]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.1" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" unit="m" value="41.0">41 m</quantity>
depth on detritic sand (
<figureCitation id="71F42A583F19FF8EFD75FE85FD19FEFC" box="[660,761,259,285]" captionStart="FIGURE 49" captionStartId="43.[151,250,1953,1977]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,730,1929]" captionTargetId="figure-221@43.[151,1436,730,1929]" captionTargetPageId="43" captionText="FIGURE 49. A) Freshly dead coloration of Buenia massutii, photo by M. Kovačić, Mallorca, Balearic Islands, Spain. B) Buenia cf. massutii live coloration in its natural habitat, photo by X. Rufray, Saint-Raphaël, Southern France." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6601721" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6601721/files/figure.png" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Fig. 49B</figureCitation>
) might be this species (
<bibRefCitation id="8D5E4B2C3F19FF8EFBE1FE85FB32FEFC" author="Rufray, X. &amp; Pillon, R. &amp; Louisy, P." box="[1024,1234,259,285]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" refId="ref64060" refString="Rufray, X., Pillon, R. &amp; Louisy, P. (2021) Signalisation de / Record of Buenia massutii, 03 December 2021 (obs. 17 October 2020, photo  6013). Fish Watch Forum, Louisy, P. &amp; Francour, P. (Ed.) Available from: https: // www. fish-watch. org (accessed 4 December 2021)" type="url" year="2021">
Rufray 
<emphasis id="DBBBEACF3F19FF8EFBB6FE85FB68FEFC" box="[1111,1160,259,285]" italics="true" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">et al</emphasis>
. 2021
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E97036DD3F19FF8EFF26FEA1FE30FE68" blockId="44.[151,1437,151,393]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">
